title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) growth rate in Finland 2024
yAxis: GDP growth compared to previous year
summary: In general GDP growth compared to previous year has fallen over the Year.
GDP growth compared to previous year is slightly decreasing from 2014 to 2015.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum GDP growth compared to previous year, about 0.63 was reported at Year 2014
The lowest GDP growth compared to previous year, of value 0.5 was reported at Year 2015
